    - 01-fix_manpage.patch, 03-fix_random_seed.patch,
      04-fix_exit_code.patch, 05-fix_spelling_error.patch,
      07-implement_reset_to_permanent_MAC.patch,
      09-change_default_behaviour.patch merged upstream, removed
